video.title: What's CS 124 Honors?
video.msg:
Take the following steps to join the course!
1) JOIN THE DISCORD (NEW LINK! ): https://discord.gg/TqEZ8NnT6v
2) Sign up for the class
Non James Scholars: Sign up for the class on self-service (CS199-124)
James Scholars: Fill out the HCLA agreement for CS 124
Everyone: Fill out this Google Form to confirm your enrollment https://forms.gle/4rB694Tm3t16aNEQ8
3) Enroll in the course on PrairieLearn https://www.prairielearn.org/pl/enroll
CS 124H: Freshman Honors: Introduction to Computer Science I
